1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
ظآزI defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortalityظآز

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
ظآزAt last you say
we've been apart too longظآز

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
ظآزUnwilling, unyielding, I won't let goظآز

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
ظآزWith you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a streamظآز

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
ظآزIf heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vesselظآز

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
ظآزIf it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Daoظآز

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
ظآزEven if countless stars
turn into my foesظآز

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
ظآزTo grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long nightظآز

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 22=

11
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:02,799
Ningxue!

12
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,959
So all these ten thousand years,

13
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,920
you've been trapped here.

14
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,159
Ningxue!

15
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:35,599
Ningxue.

16
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,319
Don't worry.

17
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,920
I will get you out of here.

18
00:01:45,655 --> 00:01:49,076
(Ten Thousand Years Ago)

19
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:59,560
It's been ages since the Immortal Realm
looked this beautiful.

20
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,560
That curse on you is fierce.

21
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,000
but I've infused you

22
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,039
a breath of my spiritual energy.

23
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:19,360
It should buy you
three hundred more years.

24
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:21,560
Ningxue,

25
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,719
I'm going into seclusion now.

26
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,919
I hope to break into
the Heavenly God Realm

27
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,479
by then,

28
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,759
and lift this curse for you.

29
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:32,080
But all I want is for you to be safe.

30
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,960
Even if the Heavenly Dao descends...

31
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,159
I won't

32
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,280
let anyone take you from me.

33
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,680
I have one last wish.

34
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:55,879
Ningxue.

35
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:57,719
Ningxue!

36
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:04,120
No.

37
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,080
That demon remnant

38
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,039
triggered the curse early.

39
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,639
Ningxue, I'm not leaving you.

40
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,280
Ningxue...

41
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:18,719
Ningxue!

42
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,439
Hang in there.

43
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,240
I'll get you out.

44
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,879
Ningxue.

45
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,759
How are you feeling?

46
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,639
My Lord, the Holy Maiden..

47
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,960
Ningxue!

48
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:12,560
Ningxue.

49
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:18,959
Su Wubing.

50
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,959
You're finally awake.

51
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,720
I remember now.

52
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,560
I remember everything.

53
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,399
So

54
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,079
much time has passed.

55
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,879
That's great.

56
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,439
Your curse is finally broken.

57
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:49,639
But won't that draw the Heavenly Dao?

58
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:53,680
Maybe it hasn't noticed yet.

59
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:54,680
Or...

60
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:56,439
My Lord,

61
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,560
we should leave now.

62
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:00,000
Let's go.

63
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,920
This...?

